        <abstract> 
<p>Sends FS some specimens of harvesting ants along with the observations of their habits made by Mary Treat. If the facts are new, he believes that Mrs Treat would be gratified by their being mentioned before the Entomological Society. [See <hi rend="doubleUnderline">11422</hi>.]</p> 
